# Common UI Patterns & Examples

## Dashboard Layouts

### KPI Dashboard
**Use case**: Display key metrics at a glance

**Structure**:
- Grid of metric cards (3-4 columns)
- Each card shows: value, label, trend indicator
- Charts below for detailed trends
- Filters at top for date range/segments

**Visual hierarchy**:
- Largest text for metric values (24-32px)
- Trend indicators in color (green up, red down)
- Labels in muted color (11px uppercase)

### Analytics Dashboard
**Components**:
- Top navigation with date picker
- Sidebar filters
- Main area: mixed chart types (line, bar, pie)
- Summary cards above charts
- Table below with pagination

## Form Layouts

### Single-Column Form
**Best for**: Short forms (3-7 fields), mobile-first

```
[Label]
[Input field spanning full width]
[Helper text]

[Label]
[Input field]

[Submit button full width]
```

### Two-Column Form
**Best for**: Longer forms with related field pairs

```
[First Name]      [Last Name]
[Email]           [Phone]
[Address line 1]
[Address line 2]
[City]            [State]  [Zip]

[Cancel] [Submit]
```

### Multi-Step Form
**Best for**: Complex forms (10+ fields)

**Components**:
- Progress indicator at top (steps 1/4, 2/4, etc.)
- Single step visible per screen
- Back + Next/Submit buttons
- Save draft option
- Summary screen at end

## Navigation Patterns

### Top Navigation
**Use case**: Few sections (3-7), desktop-focused

```
[Logo] [Nav Item] [Nav Item] [Nav Item]     [Search] [Profile]
```

### Sidebar Navigation
**Use case**: Many sections, hierarchical

```
[Logo]
[Section 1]
  [Sub-item]
  [Sub-item]
[Section 2]
[Section 3]
```

### Tab Navigation
**Use case**: Multiple views of same object

```
[Overview] [Details] [History] [Settings]
[Tab content area]
```

### Breadcrumbs
**Use case**: Deep hierarchies

```
Home > Category > Subcategory > Current Page
```

## Data Display Patterns

### Table with Actions
**Features**:
- Column headers sortable (show arrow on hover)
- Row hover state
- Checkbox for bulk selection
- Action buttons/menu per row
- Pagination or infinite scroll at bottom
- Search/filter at top

### Card Grid
**Use case**: Visual content, products, media

**Layout**:
- Responsive grid (1-4 columns based on width)
- Card: image + title + metadata + action
- Hover: slight elevation + shadow increase
- Loading: skeleton cards

### List with Preview
**Use case**: Email, messages, files

**Structure**:
- Left: scrollable list of items
- Right: selected item detail view
- Active item highlighted in list
- Responsive: stack on mobile

## Modal & Overlay Patterns

### Confirmation Modal
```
[X close]

[Icon]
Are you sure you want to delete this?
This action cannot be undone.

[Cancel] [Delete]
```

### Form Modal
- Title at top with close button
- Form fields in body
- Footer with Cancel + Submit
- Close on backdrop click or Escape key

### Drawer/Slide-over
**Use case**: Secondary content, filters, settings

- Slides in from right (or left)
- Overlay backdrop
- Close button at top
- Content scrollable
- Wider than modal (400-600px)

### Toast/Notification
**Use case**: Temporary feedback

- Fixed position: top-right or bottom-right
- Auto-dismiss after 3-5 seconds
- Colored left border (success/error/info)
- Close button optional
- Stack multiple toasts

## Search Patterns

### Instant Search
- Search input with icon
- Results appear as you type (after 2-3 chars)
- Dropdown below input with results
- Highlight matching text
- Keyboard navigation (up/down arrows, enter to select)
- Show "No results" state

### Advanced Search
- Simple input initially
- "Advanced" toggle reveals filters
- Filters: dropdowns, checkboxes, date pickers
- Applied filters shown as removable pills
- Clear all option

## Settings Page Patterns

### Tabbed Settings
```
[General] [Security] [Notifications] [Billing]

[Setting group title]
[Setting row: label + toggle/input + description]
[Setting row]

[Setting group title]
[Setting row]
```

### Grouped Settings
- Each section in a card
- Section heading
- Settings as rows within card
- Save button per section or global save at bottom

## Empty States

### No Data Yet
```
[Illustration or icon]
No items yet
Get started by creating your first item.
[Create Item button]
```

### No Search Results
```
[Search icon]
No results for "query"
Try different keywords or filters.
[Clear search button]
```

### Error State
```
[Error icon]
Something went wrong
We couldn't load this data.
[Retry button]
```

## Loading States

### Skeleton Screen
- Gray placeholder boxes matching final layout
- Subtle shimmer animation
- Preserves layout dimensions

### Spinner
- Centered in container
- Size appropriate to context (16-32px)
- Optional "Loading..." text below

### Progress Bar
- For known duration tasks
- Shows percentage complete
- Optional time remaining estimate

## Onboarding Patterns

### Welcome Tour
- Modal or spotlight highlighting features
- 3-5 steps maximum
- Skip tour option
- Progress dots at bottom
- Finish button on last step

### Empty State Onboarding
- First time user sees empty state
- Quick tips or tutorial
- Sample data option
- Video or GIF demonstrating usage

## Profile & Account Patterns

### Profile Header
```
