[Name] [Edit button]
[Email/username]
[Bio/description]

[Tab navigation: Posts | Following | Followers]
```

### Account Settings
- Avatar upload with preview
- Form fields for name, email, etc.
- Password change section
- Danger zone (delete account) at bottom in red

## Feedback & Rating Patterns

### Star Rating
- 5 clickable stars
- Hover to preview rating
- Half-star support optional
- Show average rating + count

### Feedback Form
```
How was your experience?
[😞] [😐] [😊]

Tell us more (optional)
[Text area]

[Submit feedback]
```

## Responsive Patterns

### Mobile Menu
- Hamburger icon top-left or top-right
- Full-screen or slide-out menu
- Close X or back button
- Stack navigation items vertically

### Desktop → Mobile Transformations
- Grid → single column
- Sidebar → bottom tabs or hamburger
- Table → cards or horizontal scroll
- Multi-column form → single column
- Large modals → full-screen

## Accessibility Checklist

- [ ] All interactive elements keyboard accessible
- [ ] Focus indicators visible
- [ ] Color not the only indicator (use icons + text)
- [ ] Alt text on images
- [ ] ARIA labels on icon buttons
- [ ] Proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
- [ ] Form labels associated with inputs
- [ ] Error messages announced to screen readers
- [ ] Sufficient color contrast (4.5:1 minimum)
- [ ] Touch targets 44x44px minimum
